newsitem.title: MEXICO: Mexico TIIE 28-day rate rises to 26.20 pct.
newsitem.headline: Mexico TIIE 28-day rate rises to 26.20 pct.

text.p: Mexico's 28-day interbank interest rate, known as the TIIE, rose to 26.20 percent on Thursday compared to Wednesday's rate of 25.945 percent, the Mexican Stock Exchange said.
The TIIE is a market-weighted average interbank rate.
